Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Shevchenko's affairs
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bv5k
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 Oct 1978
Mistress of defector Shevchenko claims that she is being paid with CIA money. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.